$$ ;pl1 : f1 channel - power level for pulse (default)
$$ ;pl12: f2 channel - power level for CPD/BB decoupling
$$ ;pl13: f2 channel - power level for second CPD/BB decoupling
$$ ;p1 : f1 channel -  90 degree high power pulse
